<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>1) Personally, I think that he's right. In my mind, this all makes perfect sense. Why do they have numbers and not names? Because they never had names to begin with. Why aren't they allowed contact with SCPs or even in a site with one? Because cross-testing SCPs is frowned upon. Why can they access any information they want? Because there's no point in hiding it from them.<br />
2) I predict that someone from the Foundation will be waiting for him there, likely with a loaded gun in their hands. Once the job has been done, the Agent will take the briefcase back to the O5.</p>
