<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Hide</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>But after all, there is no canon. I could be right, I could be dead wrong. Regardless, this is now one of my favorite Tales on the site. Upvoted.</p>

